id: customer-escalation-root
name: Customer Escalation Cabinet
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: Converts customer escalation chaos into a structured packet — incident header, timeline, customer impact, root-cause status, owner plan, comms log, and resolution plan — so every escalation is handled with the same rigor, not whoever is loudest in Slack. Three agents replace the ad-hoc Slack threads, manual Jira summaries, and support fire drills.
